high_descs: Turn left to exit the bedroom to walk into the dining room on the right to face the diningtable.
Pick up the potato out of the bowl on the table.
Turn around to face the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave to heat and take it out.
Turn around and take a left turn to face the right side of the diningtable.
Place the potato in front of the kettle on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated Potato on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Walk through the living room and into the kitchen then up to the diningtable.
Pick up the potato from the plate on the kitchen table.
Turn around and carry the potato to the microwave.
Place the potato into the microwave then retrieve after heating it.
Turn around and carry the potato to the far end of the diningtable by the opposite doorway.
Place the potato on to the diningtable next to the teapot.
anns.task_desc: Placing a potato onto the dining table that has been heated in the microwave.

high_descs: Go straight, turn left and then proceed to turn right and make a turn right and then turn around and walk straight, turn right towards the dining table
Pick up potato from the dining table
Turn right and head straight, turn left and then turn right towards the microwave
Place potato inside microwave and then take it out
Turn right and go straight, turn right and make a turn right and then proceed to turn left towards the dining table
Place the potato on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Place potato inside microwave and placing it in dining table
